de.ityx.mediatrix.data

Class OperatorLogRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.OperatorLogRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Object>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LogEntry

    public class OperatorLogRecord
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<Object>
    Many of the operator actions are saved for the processing objects. E.g. if the operator completed a question, the action saved as completed. The log is seen in the tab "log".
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
